{"id":"75b38c876a58011b075a7173dc8f84f5fbc4fb0ca90e1ddc0e6dd469c76929bd","text":"Licensing（许可）"}
{"id":"420e2d4380e8b92ab6a139872c3b38407f2b30f4843c9f97de79cd0f394925e6","text":"Stylized Looks（风格化外观）"}
{"id":"b61c577d1d94fce070444cd2510a985ffaf8bcca2c006a167ef521c3a6bbc980","text":"仅面向 RenderMan 的商业客户提供。"}
{"id":"82a3077efa0b253963ecb825a2e5bc18da7ef465ba24c4415fb3cb4212c6c524","text":"创新的 Stylized Looks 工具集让 RenderMan 能够生成超越照片写实的图像。艺术家可以渲染出看起来像卡通、插画或水彩的图像。这个灵活系统可用于创建独特外观，唯一限制只是想象力。"}
{"id":"320fef86610825ac82d7e61a9e8bfb4a1c63616bb5be532d28d0724a873705cb","text":"RenderMan 27 Stylized Looks 新特性"}
{"id":"011c2032237079fd4e17a74d42c7e7257dc9caf5cde2696ebc5d517f26a8ec52","text":"XPU 中的新 Filters（过滤器）"}
{"id":"4abf2a3ca953a40cb1d877a4a3fb3fd6c057717f1fbe779735b202137c7b0004","text":"PxrStylized"}
{"id":"5de7e86e12632fb253f7bac84a5f9da659d086c00d5b43518b9fca2b736e4400","text":"LinesXPU"}
{"id":"d082e56321fa677b0303d0ba6e41233d87d093fb1b4270f15795f0e04f9ad26a","text":"CanvasXPU"}
{"id":"1f4564cfafef255bf4ee12fbf2130061338a7a78e0e1d8b733413cbca43f676b","text":"HatchingSampleXPU"}
{"id":"0fcb7c563173e974359e94324c9251d1fdd898a5ef3b62d2efe566ee1d5cd310","text":"PainterlyBrushXPU"}
{"id":"c727eb5b5bd96dc48c926b905f62a37db007a342a13d4ae7930a86e1523ccc0e","text":"ToonXPU"}
{"id":"3886a52baa5850551e5ec6f1f8a34502a15f0ada0b418927fcfcf971cddfac0c","text":"XPU 与 RIS 中的新 Shaders（着色器）"}
{"id":"3dcb723b69c70dcafd0455708160cef51b28468166c929b25933ddee290098e4","text":"PainterlyBrushControl"}
{"id":"bd18a2b0e2198d18e2a22adc67281967b61a899c79f6f474ec38df0c869c5595","text":"LightControl"}
{"id":"0df4aaad184d79951f86e06c7a3655efc63a44c9464a6b47ea820a52e051bd1d","text":"(RM 27.2)"}
{"id":"d33b4c1f750beb207597ca01d6218ec08f04ea01a9a8c2e82375bc430dcdd9e9","text":"LinesControl"}
{"id":"05eb086ab319a9fbcd4728d7fe3aba721a1ae4e40ad1c92c81298652e95907d6","text":"HatchControl"}
{"id":"389ea83eb8952dd564e49a7f642769441cd6f3c6c1612ff09c28d96479bf51b5","text":"XPU 与 RIS 中更新的 Shaders（着色器）"}
{"id":"32d7e82082479b8cb546187ff0af11e4915e4d17bc28e02dca7425288b79badd","text":"Control（控制）"}
{"id":"e5965589f9be207303ff77ef683aa870cb2699af8f09a66eb4f52a80a2a66dd9","text":"Stylized Looks 亮点："}
{"id":"0904948219fa8c7bf3070db1903c71dd1d9c554d692a9b0e787f57b274129841","text":"在 RenderMan 中渲染，再使用 Stylized Looks 后处理"}
{"id":"fab79919293df071eb060784a14eabb7fa7b6a6c02eaba242c63260cdf6bcd1d","text":"Stylized Looks 是一种逐像素后处理，会在图像渲染完成后（或 IPR session 期间）应用，由 3 种不同 Display Filters（PxrStylizedToon / PxrStylizedLines / PxrStylizedHatching）处理。"}
{"id":"0cd7e53e3632f8f5014570c5bee452833f43eec8ba913c4b418f3e4c2ec8ecfa","text":"使用强大的 RenderMan 工具集中所有工具创建场景，包括 PxrSurface、Lama 和 RenderMan lights，然后将其转换为 Stylized Looks！"}
{"id":"8db693c9edfbe71e9f3a3fceaa80e3e6d9f8bfa95a3a06bc2d3368a5112df056","text":"在一次渲染中 Mix（混合）照片写实与风格化！"}
{"id":"06ea9905a1a888aa59724bb6bb26a551af7d79f8a54ed3b3d3ff98ae6387bb7e","text":"使用 RenderMan Lights 控制照片写实与风格化之间的过渡，创建出色图像。"}
{"id":"8378406c0b94f0e187e8ea0380aa11befaadc6a5e15e9b4bae741a675ce1579f","text":"例如，使用 PxrRectLight 的光束为照片写实渲染添加排线。光线照到哪里，哪里就会应用排线。"}
{"id":"5ab859c5be503b9562e60ab178f80de9a026309dd4eb0cb9297fc46c7790c87f","text":"创建你自己的纹理集"}
{"id":"1197a0dc2256114597a35b662528eb7cf2871509c39b8e872e404daa11c54451","text":"Stylized Looks 不仅随附多个纹理预设，也允许你创建并使用自己独特的纹理集。"}
{"id":"ad1046f4438938ba674d2d5651a845e49f93de3f7febb0f302b20c36f8153761","text":"需要查看某种具体 NPR 效果？没问题，创建你自己的排线纹理集！"}
{"id":"0101e407e6499b2106e57452a7013d20d5fdd218bff16c8e518c56058906cfe0","text":"Toon + Illustrative/Hatching Lighting + Lines"}
{"id":"2562fd93265d32143922a3085716562c6bc7730bf561f6d49a78274785a85b6f","text":"Toon"}
{"id":"d269f269a4dc1b22fd3f395ee61a4a95121234762ed17505690ec1ae28484e42","text":"：按每个 light 量化任意 signal（diffuse、spec、refraction 等），并可控制阶数"}
{"id":"e7b296a9d906696bec435ee1e9936a1aac70b8cf47f11927aaae4f8c3dcad364","text":"Illustrative Hatching Lighting（插画式排线照明）："}
{"id":"f4471b5cbad333dc180076ae35d985c3f3ca22d629a809e3bc12e8730e1e0d44","text":"根据灯光或 camera depth 动态生成，用于插画式光影渲染"}
{"id":"3b26a5427458edd20c9ec7f0954847adb8e0e692f739cc1bca3ab7438bc9c171","text":"Lines"}
{"id":"fe52a3f36037d8be03173322c6e4bdf02e2fa61fb035ec0ce41225d9e48eb5b2","text":"：线稿功能，可按 lighting 控制线条粗细，按自定义逐对象设置控制线条粗细；线条颜色可由 albedo、lighting 或自定义逐对象设置控制"}
{"id":"315f04f01b15b3c01c23a2d049bd185a3f7b16da132ac17510a3356e87c7a08a","text":"Mix & Match Styles（混合搭配样式）"}
{"id":"0943774e3fa85c31dcc560167d1587d1768d6937ec8eaa4e7483d2485e7a6d36","text":"Mix（混合搭配）PxrStylizedToon / PxrStylizedLines / PxrStylizedHatching display filters，创建独特而富有创意的组合"}
{"id":"01dbed95d8bb006bf84d13714a61a2f3a503eac63792046c39ac091389114a39","text":"尝试叠加多个 PxrStylizedLines，每个使用不同厚度，以创建漂亮且具有艺术感的内部和外部线稿。"}
{"id":"22ffc9c4cc6d19c5953aca15eecd34972e745083cdd0991e6b516a3806368d8e","text":"Global and per-object control（全局和逐对象控制）"}
{"id":"36f3818350b1d38e17c60ca8167204804a57b85c98eb5a15e18b8ecca10b9194","text":"将 PxrStylizedControl 附加到 PxrSurface 和 LamaSurface 节点，以控制整个场景或逐对象控制。"}
{"id":"304571923cf16284282ef325b4b58721ea9432042b1483bb4d5b730834521c83","text":"控制特定对象的不同线条粗细和着色"}
{"id":"17e4a581469d1db4c962dba99071a89b168a618dd5f321c086bba303d5fcec70","text":"导出 AOVs 以进行额外精修"}
{"id":"7649b4b2a50eb8417a10efa343cf6ac5e8adf308834526b5e7d95da624ba1913","text":"与 Stylized Looks 关联的所有 AOVs 都可以导出，以便在 RenderMan 外部进一步进行创意精修和分层处理"}
{"id":"0d30230d2c6546275fdf664e38da346271b3096d22de9e4d41823916958d98f2","text":"Getting Started with Stylized Looks"}
